cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "grpo-composer: a composable GRPO research toolkit on top of veRL"
abstract: >-
  grpo-composer is a research-friendly wrapper around veRL that makes it
  trivial to mix and match advantage estimators, policy losses, sequence
  aggregations, clipping schemes, regularizers, and reward shapers from
  recent GRPO/DAPO/Dr.GRPO-style papers.
authors:
